      <title>Setting up a new Development System</title>
      <link>/post/settingupanewsystem/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2019 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>/post/settingupanewsystem/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;setting-up-a-new-development-system-ubuntu--1804&#34;&gt;
  &lt;a class=&#34;Heading-link u-clickable&#34; href=&#34;/post/settingupanewsystem/#setting-up-a-new-development-system-ubuntu--1804&#34;&gt;Setting up a New Development System (Ubuntu &amp;gt;= 18.04)&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;mysql&#34;&gt;
  &lt;a class=&#34;Heading-link u-clickable&#34; href=&#34;/post/settingupanewsystem/#mysql&#34;&gt;MySQL&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.digitalocean.com/community/tutorials/how-to-install-mysql-on-ubuntu-18-04&#34;&gt;Digital Ocean Instructions&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-console&#34; data-lang=&#34;console&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;sudo apt update
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;sudo apt install mysql-server
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;sudo mysql_secure_installation
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Follow the steps in the Digital Ocean docs for setup&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;php&#34;&gt;
  &lt;a class=&#34;Heading-link u-clickable&#34; href=&#34;/post/settingupanewsystem/#php&#34;&gt;PHP&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-console&#34; data-lang=&#34;console&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;sudo apt-get install php7.2-CLI
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;sudo apt-get install php-xml
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;sudo apt-get install php-mysql
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;package-managers-frameworks&#34;&gt;
  &lt;a class=&#34;Heading-link u-clickable&#34; href=&#34;/post/settingupanewsystem/#package-managers-frameworks&#34;&gt;Package Managers, Frameworks&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://getcomposer.org/download&#34;&gt;Composer&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://symfony.com/download&#34;&gt;Symfony&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;code&gt;curl -sS https://get.symfony.com/cli/installer | bash&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://make.wordpress.org/cli/handbook/installing/#installing-via-composer&#34;&gt;WP-CLI&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://nodejs.org/en/&#34;&gt;Node.js&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;maybe-need&#34;&gt;
  &lt;a class=&#34;Heading-link u-clickable&#34; href=&#34;/post/settingupanewsystem/#maybe-need&#34;&gt;Maybe Need&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;curl&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;OpenSSH for ssh keys&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;nice-to-have&#34;&gt;
  &lt;a class=&#34;Heading-link u-clickable&#34; href=&#34;/post/settingupanewsystem/#nice-to-have&#34;&gt;Nice to Have&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https:/fishshell.com&#34;&gt;Fish Shell&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;development-tools&#34;&gt;
  &lt;a class=&#34;Heading-link u-clickable&#34; href=&#34;/post/settingupanewsystem/#development-tools&#34;&gt;Development Tools&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;IDE/Text Editor: &lt;a href=&#34;https://code.visualstudio.com&#34;&gt;VS Code&lt;/a&gt; Can also be accquired via App Store (Snap Store or Pop! Shop)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Graphics Program: &lt;a href=&#34;https://gimp.org&#34;&gt;Gimp&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Database GUI: &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.emma-assistant.org/&#34;&gt;Emma Database Assistant&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;FTP Client: &lt;a href=&#34;https://filezilla-project.org/&#34;&gt;FileZilla&lt;/a&gt; Also easily accquired from the platform&amp;rsquo;s App Store&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;todos&#34;&gt;
  &lt;a class=&#34;Heading-link u-clickable&#34; href=&#34;/post/settingupanewsystem/#todos&#34;&gt;ToDos&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create ssh keys: &lt;code&gt;ssh-keygen&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Apply public key to servers and version control systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;helper-apps&#34;&gt;
  &lt;a class=&#34;Heading-link u-clickable&#34; href=&#34;/post/settingupanewsystem/#helper-apps&#34;&gt;Helper Apps&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;php-codesniffer-phpcs&#34;&gt;
  &lt;a class=&#34;Heading-link u-clickable&#34; href=&#34;/post/settingupanewsystem/#php-codesniffer-phpcs&#34;&gt;PHP CodeSniffer (phpcs)&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;composer global require &amp;quot;squizlabs/php_codesniffer=*&amp;quot;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;locate and install rulesets for Symfony, Drupal8 and Wordpress
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Symfony: Follow the &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/djoos/Symfony-coding-standard#stand-alone&#34;&gt;Stand Alone&lt;/a&gt; Instructions. Cloning the repo in &lt;code&gt;~/.composer/vendor/escapestudios&lt;/code&gt; is a good place as other coding standards files end up in this vendor dir.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drupal 8: &lt;code&gt;composer global require drupal/coder&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Wordpress: Like Symfony follow the &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/WordPress/WordPress-Coding-Standards#standalone&#34;&gt;Stand Alone&lt;/a&gt; instructions. Clone into &lt;code&gt;~/.composer/vendor/wpcs&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Add the rulesets with:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-console&#34; data-lang=&#34;console&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;phpcs --config-set installed_paths ~/.composer/vendor/escapestudios,~/.composer/vendor/drupal,~/.composer/vendor/wpcs
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;NOTE&lt;/strong&gt; there are no spaces around the commas.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;vs-code-extentions&#34;&gt;
  &lt;a class=&#34;Heading-link u-clickable&#34; href=&#34;/post/settingupanewsystem/#vs-code-extentions&#34;&gt;VS Code Extentions&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;PHP IntelliSense&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;phpcs by Ioannis Kappas&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Git Lens&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Twig&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;XML Tools&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;ESLint&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prettier - Code Formatter&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</description>
